The camera-ready copy of your paper is required before {Config->cameraReadyDeadline}. You can upload your final version from the author console.
Please note that any delay may prevent the inclusion of your paper in the proceedings. Follow the instructions found at the {Config->confAcronym} site in order to prepare your final version.
The {Config->confAcronym} site also provides all necessary information for conference registration and hotel accommodation.
